Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Tufayl reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cSpeak to people only according to their level of knowledge. Would you like for Allah and His Messenger to be denied?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 127 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0637\u064f\u0651\u0641\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0645\u064a\u0631\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33900,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/09\/prophet-blessings-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":1827,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: The Prophet sends blessings on the charitable","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Abi Awfa reported: When people came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, to give charity, he would say, \u201cO Allah, send blessings upon the household of these people.\u201d My father came to him with charity and he said, \u201cO Allah, send blessings upon the household\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/former-enemies-embrace-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":1827,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Former enemies, prisoners embra